    ratings: 4,
  },
];

function Product() {
  return (
    <>
      <div className="Product">
        {Products.map((product) => (
          <div className="product_y">
            <Products_Details product={product} />
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </>
  );
}
export default Product;
